  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/c855f89a689f25c9bde1c1183c8c1fad.poster.avif?t=1773430894\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/c855f89a689f25c9bde1c1183c8c1fad.webm?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/c855f89a689f25c9bde1c1183c8c1fad.mp4?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>COMBOLITE combines roguelike deckbuilders and autobattlers in a unique way.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/a8ce37f342331142af3e13e52e330db6.poster.avif?t=1773430894\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/a8ce37f342331142af3e13e52e330db6.webm?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/a8ce37f342331142af3e13e52e330db6.mp4?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What do you do in COMBOLITE?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start every round by acquiring more weapons for your deck. <strong>Each weapon has unique stats, some inflict status effects, which you can use to create synergies between weapons!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>gems and buffs</strong> to boost the damage of your weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/26d89904c4ce38be23dde401710413bd.poster.avif?t=1773430894\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/26d89904c4ce38be23dde401710413bd.webm?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/26d89904c4ce38be23dde401710413bd.mp4?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your weapons attack in a set order, one at a time.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > This game is all about creating the <strong>optimal sequence of weapons</strong>, finding cool combinations and synergies in an attempt to deal as much damage as possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/29d8c9a55d2c758f3e0384f518c9623b.poster.avif?t=1773430894\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/29d8c9a55d2c758f3e0384f518c9623b.webm?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/29d8c9a55d2c758f3e0384f518c9623b.mp4?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HIT THE BALL AND BREAK THE GAME!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I've seen millions of damage done, someone hit <strong>13 BILLION damage</strong> in a single turn! You're encouraged to <strong>break this game,</strong> and with <strong>multiplicative buffs</strong> this isn't hard to do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you have to be quick! <strong>The target damage</strong> keeps increasing every turn, and if you can't deal enough damage, then you'll be thrown back to the main menu!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/5a4bbfd2558fdba53ba3b70eaf3359ba.poster.avif?t=1773430894\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/5a4bbfd2558fdba53ba3b70eaf3359ba.webm?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/5a4bbfd2558fdba53ba3b70eaf3359ba.mp4?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLOIT the buffs you get!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>These buffs make a certain category of weapons stronger, or provide an overall buff to the player, like increased shop luck.</strong> <strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You get these after <strong>every third fight</strong>, buying <strong>loot bags</strong> in the shop, opening <strong>treasure chests</strong> and by <strong>completing objectives</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/19c4361e7d5127c679528319964ec762.poster.avif?t=1773430894\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/19c4361e7d5127c679528319964ec762.webm?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/19c4361e7d5127c679528319964ec762.mp4?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is a combo?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combos are defined by a sequence of 3 directions and a reward for pulling them off.</strong>  <br>Each weapon attacks in one of 8 directions, and you can execute a combo by placing them in your deck in the correct order.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 categories of weapons, with a total of 44 weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 collectable buffs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >448 combos with 4 different special rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 difficulty settings to make your runs even more interesting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/02d4f13437ceba06eb4d7e4ab6594925.poster.avif?t=1773430894\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/02d4f13437ceba06eb4d7e4ab6594925.webm?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499540/extras/02d4f13437ceba06eb4d7e4ab6594925.mp4?t=1773430894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
